Package io.nextweb.nodes

Interface Summary
Bytes A node which can hold any arbitrary byte data.
Json A simple wrapper for Json data.
Port Defines an access pathway to a node (consisting of the nodes reference and the secret Token required to access the node.
Token A security authorization.
